        "type": "editorialWithImage",
        "id": "bb011c32-bff8-4274-b117-24349427434c",
        "alias": "Scenario Planning",
        "title": "",
        "content": "**Scenario planning** takes a different approach to traditional planning in that it looks at how different aspects of a situation could relate under different circumstances.",
        "buttons": [
          {
            "component": "Button",
            "content": "Continue",
            "sectionId": "d93d2dc4-937c-4d4e-9a82-46fae40b152e"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "editorialWithImage",
        "id": "d93d2dc4-937c-4d4e-9a82-46fae40b152e",
        "alias": "Scenario Planning 2",
        "content": "Scenario planning sees planning as a collective learning and takes into account:\n\n1. Things you know\n2. Things you know you don't know\n3. Things you don't know that you don't know",
        "buttons": [
          {
            "component": "Button",
            "content": "Next",
            "sectionId": "60d22a31-f15d-4326-a32a-a9315002b56a"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "editorialWithImage",
        "id": "60d22a31-f15d-4326-a32a-a9315002b56a",
        "alias": "Scenario Planning 3",
        "content": "Using scenario planning makes your work more **resilient** as it helps you **adapt** to the situation and see multiple ways of pursuing a goal.",
        "buttons": [
          {
            "component": "NextConversationButton",
            "variant": "primary",
            "conversationId": "79bd290e-cce7-4323-b2c9-e9b59f7f59b2",
            "content": "Let's practice this"
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "root": "bb011c32-bff8-4274-b117-24349427434c"
